{"tid":1635204,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"《突發》屯門要人呀","createTime":"2019-10-07T12:28:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T13:10:18.000Z","uid":205179,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"26af0d46b07f5a78d0a57a795bc0023265b6ac3f","tid":1635204,"uid":205179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:28:42.000Z","msg":"大會堂都未企滿！快啲黎啦手足"},{"pid":"f42049200aa3a8942422e4d4bfa54fef12d20b83","tid":1635204,"uid":205179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:28:50.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"fe26c86d26c2ea7234d9614a23c12ab985fc00db","tid":1635204,"uid":205179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:29:02.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"082ff657e0e29c8b71361d47e7f260c0a3e8ad2b","tid":1635204,"uid":205179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:29:12.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"80cb71b021418b0c0c32574f7982535390d5643e","tid":1635204,"uid":280136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:29:58.000Z","msg":"【facebook戰線】大家一齊report曬D垃圾page，等佢地重蹈點新聞嘅覆轍<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eewfbS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eewfbS</a><br />\n<br />\n【地方的手足需要進化】麻煩大家入黎溫下書，睇下烏克蘭係E個時候做左D咩<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ejgzzS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ejgzzS</a>"},{"pid":"a4e4d97bc9cf935799fa117053a20da528533950","tid":1635204,"uid":160842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:34:03.000Z","msg":"勿拆黨鐵！！全民被罷工！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1633581\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1633581</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n罷工係對個政權最撚有衝擊既抗爭手法，但三罷做左咁撚多次，都係得8.5成功，因為計劃左好撚耐，對香港人黎講，個個都只想被罷工，到呢個地步，你仲想做休息撚，而唔乘勝追擊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n三樣香港人應同樣憎恨既野：<br />\n政府、黑警、黨鐵<br />\n<br />\n呢三樣先係主線<br />\n你個啲乜鳩紅藍店，我理撚得你幾時搞？<br />\n個啲要休息，冇問題，但咁撚樣都唔食住上，令到全港自動罷工，咁我真係代表我全力支持既香港政府多謝你為香港既經濟服務<br />\n<br />\n唔撚係話和理非冇用，但勇和齊上齊落唔撚得？"},{"pid":"8c50d9ecc0b4b0e8d671f3b4f88e5c70015f1846","tid":1635204,"uid":164585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:35:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"924a83a91b6c2085a1ab27bbcd62cc2e0c306b0f","tid":1635204,"uid":18452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:40:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fee30947946a65af90a0189f25c9a0ddf57fdc00","tid":1635204,"uid":252973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:41:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d1ec00946f7f2bf3f2601e6f852002466b543eca","tid":1635204,"uid":207263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:41:58.000Z","msg":"屌 要人"},{"pid":"0d1ed246d56ff75fadfd64d4a1430fc661817fff","tid":1635204,"uid":319562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:46:04.000Z","msg":"開波未 等左好奈啦！！<br />\n牛牛出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57c05a039800a037f7799ba65abb80b6765a45fe","tid":1635204,"uid":167192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T13:01:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"60bab66b901e02f84ec131e4dd37d57d69bb1d81","tid":1635204,"uid":81996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T13:01:44.000Z","msg":"街坊幫手呀"},{"pid":"0300804c2d5e94d3fb14b245f7769eb7f09271e6","tid":1635204,"uid":167192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T13:01:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d52728c267badfb284dc4e9bc4b07991478d9872","tid":1635204,"uid":133202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T13:02:02.000Z","msg":"邊到要人?"},{"pid":"9f6695d2271b60a69c383d3a5e2f64590697f5f8","tid":1635204,"uid":319562,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T13:04:50.000Z","msg":"大會堂呀呀呀呀呀~"},{"pid":"48683ec4aa7622fa606d08d7645ade12511b9835","tid":1635204,"uid":167192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019